FieldTypesBundle CHANGELOG
==========================

20200110 (mw) – Adjustments for 2019.03
---------------------------------------

Removed some deprecated calls, as well as changed some calls in the
"Type" class.

20180320 (mw) – Added missing `ezmatrix` field type
---------------------------------------------------

Because the legacy `ezmatrix` field type hasn't been implemented in Symfony, we
have implemented it ourselves.

It basically returns the whole Matrix, so you can access all data via (multiple)
arrays.


20200407 (fW) bugfix search indexing for cjwgeoaddress => no indexing => but no errors
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Cjw/FieldTypesBundle/Resources/config/fieldtypes.yml

    # fix search indexing:
    # Exception Class: OutOfBoundsException
    # Exception Message: No type registered for cjwgeoaddress.
    # https://symfony.fi/ez-platform-tip/field-type-gotcha-no-type-registered-for
    ezpublish.fieldtype.indexable.cjwgeoaddress:
        class: "%ezpublish.fieldType.indexable.unindexed.class%"
        tags:
            - {name: ezpublish.fieldType.indexable, alias: cjwgeoaddress}
